      "type": "rich-text-about-fdn",
      "settings": {
        "title": "",
        "text": "<p><strong>Every day from December 6th until December 24th, Grand River Hospital Foundation will be offering gift wrapping at Conestoga Mall in support of Grand River Hospital!<\/strong><\/p><p>The gift wrapping station has its own storefront near Entrance #1 between IceWave Jewellers and Freedom Mobile, directly across from Children's Place and Old Navy. Our incredible team of volunteers will be there every day during mall hours to help you with your holiday wrapping and receive donations. Because even during the holidays, care never stops at Grand River Hospital. <\/p>",
