        "title": "Details",
        "text": "<p><strong>Dates: <\/strong>December 6th - December 24th<br\/><strong>Times: <\/strong>Monday to Friday from 10 a.m. to 9 p.m. \/ Saturdays from 10 a.m. to 7 p.m. \/ Sundays from 10 a.m. to 6 p.m.<br\/><strong>Location:  <\/strong>Conestoga Mall (550 King St N. Waterloo, ON)<br\/><br\/><em><strong>The gift wrapping station has its own storefront just inside the main entrance on King St N (Entrance #1) directly across from Children's Place and Old Navy, between IceWave Jewellers and Freedom Mobile.<\/strong><\/em><\/p>",
